      "description": {
        "en": "DVIA Series uses a feedback control algorithm to continuously detect vibrations and respond immediately to minimize vibrations in real-time. The feedforward control algorithm efficiently dampens ground vibrations before they are transmitted to the equipment mounted on the active vibration isolation platform.",
